<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.6">
<l>taṭattaviḻ tāmaraip poykait tāḷkaḷeṅ kālaik katuva</l>
<l>viṭattē ḷeṟintā lēpōla vētaṉai yāṟṟavum paṭṭōm</l>
<l>kuṭattai yeṭuttēṟa viṭṭuk kūttāṭa vallaveṅ kōvē</l>
<l>paṭiṟṟaiyel lāntavirn teṅkaḷ paṭṭaip paṇittaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the [lotus] stalks of the pond with big, open lotuses sting our legs,</l>
<l>we have greatly suffered pain, as if a poisonous scorpion stung [us]!</l>
<l>O our King capable of performing the kūttu-dance by taking pots and throwing [them] up!</l>
<l>Refraining from all wickedness, do grace to give [back our] silk clothes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
